               <p>I am <rs id="t17900526-15-viclabel76" type="occupation">clerk</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900526-15-victim188 t17900526-15-viclabel76"></join> to Mess. Wrights, bankers, in Covent-garden. I was robbed on the 23d of April, a little before ten, between the <placeName id="t17900526-15-crimeloc77">Foundling Hospital</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17900526-15-crimeloc77" type="placeName" value="Foundling Hospital"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17900526-15-crimeloc77" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900526-15-off74 t17900526-15-crimeloc77"></join>, and <placeName id="t17900526-15-crimeloc78">the Duke of Bolton's</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17900526-15-crimeloc78" type="placeName" value="the Duke of Bolton's"></interp>
