                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900526-15-off74 t17900526-15-crimeloc78"></join>: I was going along, I met three men who asked me for my property; they pulled my hat over my eyes; I cannot swear to their persons; my property has been found; I lost the things in the indictment; I was frightened very much, and begged they would not use me ill: I gave information at Bow-street the next day, and gave a description of the property: I saw my watch at the office in East Smithfield, about a fortnight after the robbery; I know the watch: the maker's name is 
